**Parking-Lot Preset HLD**

**What in scope:** allocate free spot in a parking lot sorting by vehicle type (motorcycle car or van).  
**Out of scope:** accessibility, payment.

![][image1]

**Leave Parking Spot**

POST/ spots/release

body {  
reservation\_id:string,  
}

**Response**

{  
success: true  
}  
{  
success: false,  
error\_msg: reservation\_not\_found  
}

**Data Model**

type SpotSize \= MOTORCYCLE | COMPACT | LARGE  
type CarType \= MOTORCYCLE | CAR| VAN

ParkingSpot {  
	\_id: unique,  
spot\_number,  
	size: SpotSize,  
	is\_free:Boolean,  
	parking\_floor: Number  
	occupied\_by: ObjectId  
}

ParkingReservation{  
plate\_number: String,  
car\_type:CarType,  
parking\_spot:ObjectId,  
status: String,  
timestamp: Date,  
}
